        <item>
            <title>1.3.5</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 12:26:09 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>66</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.5</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[- Added "Show all notes" and "Hide all notes" to the menu bar to open or hide every note at once.
- You can now turn existing text into a checklist — place the cursor before the text and type "- ".
- The Support form now keeps what you've typed and any files you've attached when you switch between Settings tabs.
- The menu bar now shows "Update available" with the new version when an update is ready to install.
- Polished menu bar wording for a cleaner, more consistent look.
]]></description>
